{"type":null,"faqId":21652,"title":"手环的防水防尘情况如何？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-indent:0.29166666in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:0.008333334in;margin-left:0.29166666in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>荣耀手环有IP57级别的防尘防水能力，可以防止一般的微尘进入手环，而且可以支持手环在小于1米的水深下静止半小时。正常使用时防溅水是没有问题的，您可以戴着手环洗手，做饭和洗澡，但是不建议您佩戴手环游泳和潜水。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果手环脏了，您也可以用水进行清洗。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果您看到手环内部有水珠，您不用担心，只需要将水珠清理干净即可，不会影响手环使用。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5353","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1427334706000,"seriesProductName":"B1-Honor","visitedTimes":55,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}